tmpfs utilities

1. make install
2. create /etc/sysconfig/tmpfs ( see e sample in etc/sysconfig )
3. create dirs as in /etc/sysconfig/tmpfs
4. add a line to /etc/fstab which is similar  to
none /home/robert/${your_ramdisk} tmpfs defaults,user,uid=${your_user},gid=users,size=512M,mode=755 0 0

for a 512M ramdisk
